{
    "name": "Glaive Rager",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>During Combat </b>The barbarian leads with trip maneuvers, seeking to trigger attacks of opportunity. He uses knockback to force creatures to advance on him again through the threatened area of his glaive.<br/><b>Base Statistics </b>When not raging, the barbarian\u2019s statistics are <b>AC </b>19, touch 12, flat-footed 18; <b>hp </b>89; <b>Fort </b>+10, <b>Will </b>+3; no bonus vs. spells and spell-like or supernatural abilities; <b>Melee </b>mwk cold iron glaive +13/+8 (1d8+4/\u00d73) or kukri +12/+7 (1d3+3/18\u201320); <b>Ranged </b>mwk composite longbow +11/+6 (1d6+3/\u00d73); <b>Str </b>16, <b>Con </b>16; <b>CMB </b>+10 (+14 trip); <b>Skills </b>Climb +6, Swim +8."
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "There is no description for this NPC."
        }
    ],
